text.tspan: Dealt with anxiety or depression by talking to friends or family, 2020
Respondents who reported that they 'felt so anxious or depressed that they could not continue their regular
daily activities as they normally would for two weeks or longer' were asked whether they ever talked to friends
or family to make themselves feel better.
